{"tid":474051,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過撞到呢啲嘢？","createTime":"2017-11-19T19:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T00:00:48.000Z","uid":17145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1228bfff189ebb87f9d74841f6e4e44a3800561","tid":474051,"uid":17145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T19:46:48.000Z","msg":"是咁的，啱啱食完宵夜，見銀包冇乜錢 <br />\n就行去最近嘅atm禁錢，見到sc atm就行入去<br />\n咁sc atm岀哂名又廢又慢，應該冇人用啦<br />\n點知行入見到兩部都有人用緊，咁我就排隊等啦<br />\n兩條友不停咁禁錢，仲要係禁一百岀一張紙<br />\n等緊嘅時候，佢地蝗語對答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗:屌你老母！兩隻蝗加垃圾atm實有排等！<br />\n當我想走嘅時，有一隻蝗讓俾我禁錢！<br />\n我禁緊錢嘅時候，隔離隻蝗仲要攞咗一疊錢岀黎<br />\n究竟呢個係咩玩法？？"},{"pid":"abb10c6587e9b6f4cbfe9754141a0b1a7c8fdaef","tid":474051,"uid":12850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T20:08:00.000Z","msg":"你肯定係人？"},{"pid":"70206c828759fef65a56560a34634905bd59093d","tid":474051,"uid":93655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T20:17:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你肯定係人？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49988a416e67f89e318b2342850a933066477fb4","tid":474051,"uid":5406,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T20:29:29.000Z","msg":"用你手指模搵你密碼"},{"pid":"582cf93b9c1af821899dbdbcfb367389ebe63008","tid":474051,"uid":155886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T00:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}